    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Get ready for a dependable ride that's perfect for your daily commute! This vehicle is in honest, fair condition and has been a reliable companion on the road. While it shows some character through normal wear and tear and minor cosmetic imperfections, it remains a sturdy and practical choice for anyone seeking value and functionality. It\u2019s a great opportunity to own a solid car that\u2019s ready to keep on going!",
