      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously sorted specimen that redefines the standard for this chassis. This isn't a mere garage queen; it is a precision-engineered machine featuring a zero-lash valvetrain and a bespoke ECU map optimized for linear torque delivery and throttle response. The suspension geometry has been perfected with high-durometer polyurethane bushings to eliminate deflection, while the cooling system has been over-engineered with a high-capacity aluminum core for total thermal stability under load. Every fluid service has been performed at half-intervals using high-zinc synthetic lubricants. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, sealed under a professional ceramic coating. This is a turn-key build for the discerning pilot who demands mechanical sympathy and peak performance. Serious inquiries only.",
